_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">73&#160;AC</a>–?\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Strong\" title=\"Lyonel Strong\">Lyonel Strong</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404201928\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.357 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1439/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 13668/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10190/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3630/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3761/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.55 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  344.596      1 -total\n 86.86%  299.319      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 86.17%  296.952      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.40%   39.294     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.36%   21.911      1 Template:S-bef\n  4.99%   17.182      3 Template:Main_other\n  4.25%   14.647      1 Template:S-bef/check\n  3.95%   13.598      7 Template:Ref\n  3.84%   13.241      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.42%   11.797      4 Template:Date\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25103-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404201928 and revision id 329831\n -->\n",
